                            "widgetType": "text-editor",
                            "settings": {
                                "editor": "<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> 21 February 2026</p><p>Thank you for shopping at <strong>SiconArt</strong>. We want you to love what you receive. If something isn't right, we'll help you as quickly and fairly as possible.</p><p>For any return, exchange, or after-sales request, please contact: <strong>support@siconart.com</strong></p><h3>1) Returns (Change of Mind)</h3><p>We accept returns for most items <strong>within 30 days of delivery</strong>, as long as the item is:</p><ul><li>Brand new, unused, and unwashed</li><li>In <strong>original packaging</strong> (box/pouch, inserts, accessories, tags, and any protective covers)</li><li><strong>Not tested with water, ink, paint, or cleaning agents</strong> (especially important for brushes)</li></ul><p><strong>Important:</strong> Please email us first. Do <strong>not</strong> send items back without authorization, as we may be unable to match the package to your order. Shipping cost to us needs to be borne by the customer.</p><h3>2) Non-Returnable Items</h3><p>To protect product quality and hygiene, we do <strong>not</strong> accept returns or exchanges for:</p><ul><li>Items showing <strong>any signs of use</strong> (e.g., brush tips altered, dampness, staining, paint residue, odor, or reshaping)</li><li><strong>Final sale / clearance</strong> items (if marked as final sale)</li><li><strong>Gift cards</strong> or downloadable/digital products (if applicable)</li><li>Returns requested <strong>after 30 days</strong> from delivery</li><li>Returns sent <strong>without prior approval</strong></li></ul><h3>3) Exchanges &amp; Replacements (Wrong / Damaged / Defective)</h3><p>If you received any of the following, we will arrange a <strong>free replacement</strong>, <strong>resend</strong>, or an appropriate solution:</p><ul><li>Wrong item / wrong variation sent</li><li>Item arrived with <strong>obvious damage</strong></li><li>Manufacturing defects</li><li>Missing parts/accessories</li><li>Severe shipping damage to packaging affecting the product</li></ul><p><strong>Please contact us within 7 days of delivery</strong> and include:</p><ul><li>Order number</li><li>Clear photos (and a short video if needed)</li><li>A brief description of the issue</li></ul><p>Email: <strong>support@siconart.com</strong></p>",
